    <div class="row align-items-center mb-5">
        <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4 mb-lg-0">
            <div class="card shadow-sm border-0 rounded-4 h-100 bg-white p-4">
                <h2 class="mb-4 fw-bold text-primary">Our Story</h2>
                <p class="lead mb-3">
                    Founded in 2025, CityExplorer was born from a passion for urban exploration and cultural discovery.
                    We believe that every city has its own unique story, hidden gems, and unforgettable experiences waiting to be discovered.
                </p>
                <p class="mb-0">
                    Our team of travel enthusiasts and local experts work tirelessly to curate the most authentic and
                    memorable city tours around the world. From bustling metropolises to charming historic towns,
                    we help travelers connect with the heart and soul of each destination.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
            <div class="bg-light rounded-circle shadow-lg d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center overflow-hidden"
                 style="width: 320px; height: 320px;">
                <img src="https://media.istockphoto.com/id/1401126607/photo/aerial-view-of-beautiful-skyscrapers-along-the-river-at-sunset-sky.jpg?s=612x612&w=0&k=20&c=pxD5s6SKlM5k5rFilSffJOeXLxzYP3EUyw4vR2pTOxQ=" alt="City"
                     style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;" />
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

    <div class="row mb-5">
        <div class="col-12">
            <h2 class="text-center mb-5 fw-bold text-primary">Our Mission & Values</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-lg rounded-4 bg-white">
                <div class="card-body text-center p-4">
                    <div class="bg-light rounded-circle p-3 mb-3 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center shadow-sm" style="width:70px; height:70px; margin:0 auto;">
                        <i class="fas fa-globe fa-2x text-primary"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-2">Global Reach</h4>
                    <p class="mb-0">CityExplorer connects travelers with unique destinations around the world, offering curated experiences across continents. With a multilingual platform and international listings, users can plan trips confidently — whether exploring popular cities or hidden gems.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-lg rounded-4 bg-white">
                <div class="card-body text-center p-4">
                    <div class="bg-light rounded-circle p-3 mb-3 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center shadow-sm" style="width:70px; height:70px; margin:0 auto;">
                        <i class="fas fa-handshake fa-2x text-primary"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-2">Local Partnership</h4>
                    <p class="mb-0">We collaborate with local guides, businesses, and cultural ambassadors to ensure authentic travel experiences. This empowers local communities while giving travelers insider access to real, on-the-ground adventures.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-lg rounded-4 bg-white">
                <div class="card-body text-center p-4">
                    <div class="bg-light rounded-circle p-3 mb-3 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center shadow-sm" style="width:70px; height:70px; margin:0 auto;">
                        <i class="fas fa-leaf fa-2x text-primary"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-2">Sustainable Tourism</h4>
                    <p class="mb-0">CityExplorer promotes eco-friendly practices by highlighting green destinations, encouraging low-impact travel, and supporting responsible tourism initiatives — helping preserve our planet for future generations of explorers.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

